---
// About section for Cyanweb Solutions
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>About Cyanweb Solutions</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p class="lead">
          Pioneering digital excellence in Perth since 1998
        </p>

        <p>
          Founded by Jonathan Huckabee and Tracii Vann, Cyanweb Solutions has been at the forefront
          of digital innovation for over 25 years. Based in Morley, Western Australia, we've helped
          countless SME businesses transform their digital presence and achieve their online goals.
        </p>

        <p>
          With over 30 years of combined IT experience, our team brings deep expertise in web development,
          digital marketing, and technology consulting. We've been online marketers and web developers
          since 1996, giving us unique insights into the evolving digital landscape.
        </p>

        <div class="stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">25+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Projects Delivered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Client Focused</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="founder-info">
          <h3>Meet Our Founder</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Jonathan Huckabee</strong> - Digital Developer & Technologist<br>
            Currently serving as Founder and IT lead at The Streets Network, Jonathan brings
            extensive experience in crafting innovative information technology solutions that
            drive business success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual">
        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Our Mission</h4>
            <p>
              Empowering businesses with cutting-edge digital solutions that drive growth,
              enhance brand presence, and deliver measurable results.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h4>Our Values</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>✓ Innovation & Excellence</li>
              <li>✓ Client Success First</li>
              <li>✓ Transparent Communication</li>
              <li>✓ Long-term Partnerships</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 80px 20px;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #0d1117;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00bcd4 0%, #0097a7 100%);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #00bcd4;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #495057;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    margin: 40px 0;
    padding: 30px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #00bcd4;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6c757d;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .founder-info {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .founder-info h3 {
    color: #0d1117;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .founder-info p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .founder-info strong {
    color: #00bcd4;
  }

  .about-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .visual-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00bcd4 0%, #0097a7 100%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 35px;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.2);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .visual-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .visual-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .visual-card p {
    color: white;
    opacity: 0.95;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .visual-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .visual-card li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .about-text h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
